    "For this component of the assessment, one (2%) tool scored Critical, 10 (18%) tools scored High, 17 (30%) tools scored Medium, 19 (33%) tools scored Low and 10 (18%) tools scored Very Low.",
    "We recommend all 'Red' scoring tools are prioritised for follow-up using interactive assessments where appropriate.",
    "Engagement with tool developers and consideration of access safeguards could be warranted if deemed necessary on further review.",
    "Furthermore, we recommend all 'Amber' tools be reviewed by technical experts to determine whether similar follow-up actions are required.",
